      "kind": "round-trip",
      "description": "delete-sheet removes exactly the named sheet ([CoreCopy, Zulu, Core] after deleting Alpha); deleting down to one sheet works; deleting the LAST sheet is refused (buried) — the survivor list proves the guard held.",
      "expr": {
        "and": [
          {
